newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 4,237 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 4,237 contracts.

text.p: Chicago Board of Trade said its Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totaled 4,237 contracts compared with 1,047 overnight Sunday.
There were 77 wheat, 1,712 corn, 1,648 soybean, 359 soymeal, 54 soyoil, one rice, 25 corn calls, four corn puts, 26 soybean calls and 331 soybean puts traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was one to 2-1/2 cents per bushel higher, corn was one to 2-1/4 cents higher and soybeans were three to 11-1/4 cents higher.
